{"tid":1350461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[低成本抗爭]全民黑衣，聲援義士","createTime":"2019-07-22T12:57:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T16:26:12.000Z","uid":108757,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b8414eded19e8c1b111b7426e2523cb9ed290ec5","tid":1350461,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:57:59.000Z","msg":"各位香港市民，抗爭係一條要大家一齊行嘅路，就算你地有負擔，都可以喺有限度情況下作出最大嘅抗爭。各位返工、出街、睇戲、食飯、落街買餸，都要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">著黑衫</span>，以示對抗爭者及抗爭運動嘅支持。只要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">成個香港都係黑衣人</span>，就全香港都變得安全，因為只要我地<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">人多</span>，就無黑社會夠膽出嚟打市民、打記者、打議員。我地要做嘅係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">將抗爭融入日常生活，將日常生活變成抗爭</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n懇請各位市民，喺有限度嘅情況下盡自己最大力量，支持抗爭運動，未來係要靠我地香港人一手一腳打返嚟，就由改變生活上嘅小小習慣開始做起。全香港人已經無得再退，只有抗爭一條出路。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">注意︰請參與者盡量帶備基本防具，眼罩、口罩、長遮、頭盔等，以策安全，自保為先。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n請同各位市民講，呼籲大家一齊參與。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QsifTC3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQsifTC3.jpg&h=b9bcc9f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nDQepKK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnDQepKK.jpg&h=37e87fac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e01407915b99607b53fe904d15ec4046df4f305e","tid":1350461,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:59:09.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"c4973246b07c3619f81b72b2b24577dd6188fa38","tid":1350461,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:01:04.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"ad1491d42ef4befbbc887b6df60fea78320f11ac","tid":1350461,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:02:01.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"543c3483e09b5e71c4162a5b7393e9d004cef7d2","tid":1350461,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r